&lt;p&gt;The Pendo Center of Excellence (CoE) sets the standard for how Pendo uses Pendo. We bring together in-app and email engagement, Product Operations, and growth strategy to ensure every team maximizes the value of the platform — and every customer receives a consistent, contextual, and high-quality experience. The CoE is a small, high-leverage team: the Head of CoE sets direction and strategic priorities, a Specialist drives day-to-day execution, and Product Operations partners on system foundations. This Lead role sits at the center of that system.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re hiring a Lead, Center of Excellence to scale the team&#39;s impact. You&#39;ll evolve the CoE from a team that launches guides and emails into a system-driven operating model that drives measurable outcomes — across onboarding, retention, support deflection, and customer lifecycle. You&#39;ll translate strategy into scalable processes, partner closely with the Head of CoE and Specialist to improve throughput without sacrificing quality, and serve as the CoE&#39;s point of collaboration for Fin-related initiatives. This is a systems-focused, impact-driven role for someone who understands not just how to use Pendo, but how to use it to move the needle.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is based in Raleigh, NC or US remote, and follows Pendo&#39;s hybrid model: in-office 3 days per week where applicable.&lt;/p&gt;
