&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;End-to-End Ownership.&lt;/strong&gt; Own your work from design through production deployment, operational monitoring, and business impact measurement. Accountability extends beyond the feature to CI/CD pipeline health, observability, cost efficiency, and domain-level outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
